<title>bạnwr ạlsẖjrẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bạnwr ạlsẖjrẗ wʿlyhạ njmẗ
 wnwrk jwạyạ mạly qlby bsmẗ
 bạḥtfl bmylạdk dy ạlạ̉ʿyạd ạ̉ʿyạdk
 wạlạnwạr tnwr ḥwạlyn ạlwlạd
 ạlqrạr- frḥẗ ạlʿyd rby lmạ sknt fy qlby
 ạ̉nạ bạhdy lk ḥby fy ywm ạlmylạd
 ạ̹nt jyt ʿlsẖạny wạ̉kẖdt mkạny
 wmlyt qlby ạ̉gẖạny fy ywm ạlmylạd
 bạḥbk yạ yswʿy mn qlby bạṣly lk
 lyk bạqdm ʿmry wbṣwty bạgẖny lk</lyrics>
</song>